f1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Ngo%E1%BA%A1n/Ngu-m%E1%BB%B9-nh%C3%A2n-th%E1%BA%A3o-h%C3%A0nh/poem-N6O2IGtXnrrxjeKqu1KwiQ">Ngu mỹ nhân thảo hành - 虞美人草行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Ngo%E1%BA%A1n/author-uWWMt6j8c6UoM1tDLnF61Q">Nguỵ Ngoạn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%C3%B3-Thanh-Th%C3%A0nh-huy%E1%BB%87n-xu%E1%BA%A5t-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%C3%B4-k%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%A0o-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-thi%E1%BA%BFu-do%C3%A3n/poem-zO770pAyJ8UphLizVeVtrw">Phó Thanh Thành huyện xuất Thành Đô, ký Đào, Vương nhị thiếu doãn - 赴青城縣出成都，寄陶王二少尹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/T%E1%BA%BF-thi%C3%AAn-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Ba-v%C4%83n/poem-mgYAjQ2Q5NsDGZNtKtk96w">Tế thiên địa văn - 祭天地文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Morikawa-Chikukei/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-L%E1%BB%A5c-nguy%E1%BB%87t-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Cung-Th%C3%A0nh-Nham-Th%E1%BB%A7-Thanh-S%C3%A2m-tam-huy%E1%BB%87n-h%E1%BA%A3i-d%E1%BA%ADt-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng/poem-xc35XtZ5fgdMRhSGHvlDBA">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - Lục nguyệt thập ngũ nhật, Cung Thành, Nham Thủ, Thanh Sâm tam huyện hải dật, trướng nhiên hữu phú - 水調歌頭－六月十五日，宮城，岩手，青森三縣海溢，悵然有賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Morikawa-Chikukei/author-_hflrw-MrPlLEBFOl7MVPA">Morikawa Chikukei</a>)<br></div>	</div>
